data.title: Council and Committee Meeting Calendar
data.text:
On January 13, 2023, the City Council adopted a Resolution establishing a new committee structure (Council file No. 23-2000). Click HERE to subscribe to agendas.

To view City Council and Council Committee Meetings prior to March 15, 2021, please visit links below

Note: This site supports all major browsers including Safari, Firefox, Chrome, and the most recent version of Microsoft Edge. For the best possible experience, Chrome is recommended. Be aware that Internet Explorer is not supported. If you are using Internet Explorer, you will need to switch to a different browser previously mentioned.
